Review Text: This is the worst place to have juice. They serve maaza for mango juice! Please refrain from going to this restaurant. So cheap customer service.

The only thing I asked was is to not add any ice or sugar. And they added both so definitely I don't like the service. Also, the order was for 2 juices and it was delivered after 2hrs. Very bad experience.

They are sellling over prices packaged fruit juices.
I ordered through zomato and when i tasted, it
wasnt fresh fruit juice. It was packaged fruit juice.
I have ordered for lemon juice and the taste is damnn bad, they have grinded the seeds also, top of that they did not add sufficient sugar
